column_description: Unique identifier for each team, serves as primary key of this table, cannot be NULL.
value_description: Universally unique identifier (UUID) used to distinguish each team.

column_description: The name or code of the team.
value_description: Example: CANAAN24004-BJ08, GS111, GS19037-BJ04, ISS24139-WH08. Represents team names or identifiers.

column_description: A description providing additional details about the team (if available).
value_description: Free-text field to describe the team, optional and nullable.
